Description:
While using Presto, if you switch to another app then return to Presto the map will disappear until you perform an action that will refresh the page.

Steps to reproduce:
1 - Open Presto
2 - While in Map view open another app
3 - Return to Presto

Expected Result:
Presto opens with the map refreshed.

Actual Result:
Presto opens but the map is no longer visible.(Video included)

Workaround:
To make the map reappear, go to the Plans or Account tabs then return to the map tab.
